Definition: The prov:endedAtTime establishes the relationship between prov:Activity and xsd:DateTime that allows one to specify the time when the activity ended.
The prov:startedAtTime establishes the relationship between prov:Activity and xsd:DateTime that allows one to specify the time when the activity started.
The brainkb:hasAssertionCategory property relates brainkb:Evidence and brainkb:Categories, specifying the classification or category that the assertion belongs to.
The brainkb:has_assertion_text property relates an eco:Assertion to an xsd:string, providing a textual excerpt of the assertion being made.
